data.description: GORGEOUS, turn-key, 4 bedroom PLUS office, 2.5 bath pool home in the very desirable DeBary Golf & Country Club! This home truly has it all, including a gorgeous custom in-ground salt water pool with pebble tec flooring, beach entry, spa, fountains and is solar heated and a NEW ROOF (2022). The spacious lot is on the CORNER and sits on .25 ACRES! As you walk in you will see just how immaculate this home has been kept. The kitchen and all bathrooms have been completely UPDATED. The kitchen has beautiful custom cabinets, custom pantry, granite countertops along with newer stainless steel appliances. The gas fireplace in the Living Room was recently refaced. The primary suite is massive, has a stylish barn door leading to the SPACIOUS primary bath which includes 2 walk in closets, vanity with custom cabinets, dual sinks and a shower featuring a multi function panel which has rain shower head, hand held nozzle, tub filler and massage jets. The pool bath and guest bath are also completely remodeled. NO CARPET, luxury vinyl plank downstairs and NEW wood floors upstairs & on stairs. The exterior has excellent CURB APPEAL, it was recently painted along with new shutters & fixtures. The BIG screened in lanai has rustic corrugated ceiling and a side view of the lake. NEW water heater just installed. TOO MANY EXTRAS to list, this is a definite MUST SEE. DeBary Plantation is conveniently located close to shopping, dining, I-4, Sunrail, the St. Johns River and is 30 minutes to Downtown Orlando or beaches (New Smyrna and Daytona). Schedule your private showing today. This property may be under audio/video surveillance.
